ore\": 0.9701662783356761, \"rank\": 0.025015403354321935, \"text\": \"United States\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This is Little's second medal of the Games, having already claimed a silver medal in the mixed 4x400m relay.\", \"from\": 667, \"to\": 775, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Little is no stranger to winning 400m races.\", \"from\": 777, \"to\": 821, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"During her time in Aggieland, she was a back-to-back-to-back national champion in the 400m hurdles, and still holds the Aggie record time for the event, setting it back in 2016.\", \"from\": 822, \"to\": 999, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 841, \"end\": 850, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bryan\\u2013College_Station\", \"score\": 0.9878074045079444, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Aggieland\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bryan\\u2013College_Station\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bryan\\u2013College_Station\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Deadmon and the USA men's 4x400m relay team also tasted the gold yet again in their relay, having won the same race in the 2020 Tokyo Games as well.\", \"from\": 1001, \"to\": 1149, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1017, \"end\": 1020, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.8070986208262001, \"rank\": 0.23897488472846096, \"text\": \"USA\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Deadmon, Christopher Bailey, Vernon Norwood, and Rai Benjamin ran their race in 2:54.43, setting a new Olympic record.\", \"from\": 1151, \"to\": 1269, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1160, \"end\": 1178, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christopher_Bailey_(fashion_designer)\", \"scor